Author: Farm2Kitchen
Title: Top Rated IEO Farm2Kitchen to Launch 2nd Round on Probit Exchange!
Body: Farm2Kitchen is an award-winning project solving a key problem identified by the UN’s World Food Programme.  Farm2Kitchen has been rated as one of the best use cases of Blockchain Technology by Industry Experts!  https://i.imgur.com/qgUIIIl.jpg  The Global Food Traceability Market is accounted for $11.25 billion in 2017 and is expected to reach $20.95 billion by 2026 growing at a CAGR of 7.15% during the forecast period.  Farm2Kitchen is revolutionizing the way food is delivered to food services, restaurants and other wholesale buyers. We are building a truly decentralized and trustless food distribution network which is powered by Blockchain technology to track the food delivery from the farm to the kitchen in order to ensure freshness and quality.  Growing consumer concern for food safety, high demand in emerging economies, stringent export regulations and the increasing penetration of modern retail, such as supermarkets and hypermarkets are some of the key factors driving the market growth.  The future is bright for food traceability. As industry adoption continues to grow, so will the significant benefits realized across the industry.  Farm2Kitchen will be a win-win for farmers, food companies and consumers.   Farm2Kitchen Token will increase in value as millions of farmers and food service operators will use the tokens for transactions on the platform.  Currently Farm2Kitchen is working with 600,000 farmers in Asia and the number is increasing day-by-day. We have been working in the food services business for past 8 years and have a team with combined experience of more than 70+ years in the fields of IT, Supply Chain, Agriculture and Food Services!
